									</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->

				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Traditional currencies like the dollar are wasteful because they require banks, the Fed, transaction fees, etc. Bitcoin removes the middle man and centralization.  People are tired of the govt bailing out banks and Wallstreet and rewarding them for taking risks.  Bitcoin makes it fair and transaction fees are near zero.  Paypal, credit cards, etc. charge 1-3% for a single transaction.  This overhead can be removed with bitcoin.  The banking industry could fall because of bitcoin.</p>
