					<div class="comment-author vcard">
						<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/04c30c6a357796c47108df3e4fa4b9f7?s=74&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D74&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-74 photo' height='74' width='74' />						<b class="fn"><a href='https://karsha.biz' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Masoud Gheysari M</a></b> <span class="says">says:</span>					</div><!-- .comment-author -->

					<div class="comment-metadata">
						<a href="http://starburst.hackerfriendly.com/?p=1530#comment-269">
							<time datetime="2011-06-28T02:22:05+00:00">
								June 28, 2011 at 2:22 am							</time>
